'''Saminalwala''' was a [[Fras]] and littermate of [[Saminalwasa]]. Both of them gave the impression of being extremely arrogant, which was in fact true. Both of the Fras' belonged to a group of [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] in the [[Sector/Legends|sector]] next to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ananuru]]. When the [[RNA brainwashing virus]] appeared in an auction on the ''[[Ananuru Express]]'', the two of them were paid by [[Secesh Trant]], who was secretly working for the [[Destabilization|Destablization branch]] of [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]], to guard her while she stole the [[Data-tape/Legends|datatape]] during the auction. While Secesh attempted to escape with the datatape, they fought off anyone trying to follow her before being beaten by a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]].

